                                    <nbsp/>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <nbsp/>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Solving steps:
                        <ol marker="1.">
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <nbsp/>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <p>
                                    <nbsp/>
                                </p>
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </sidebyside>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    The equation for the z-score of blueberry plants:
